{{> header}}
<h1>Reset your password</h1>
<p>Hi {{name}}, we received a request to reset the password for your Team Workspace account.</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin:28px 0;">
  <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="btn">Reset my password</a>
</p>
<div class="alert">
  <p>⏱ &nbsp;This link expires in <strong>{{expiresIn}}</strong>. After that you'll need to request a new one.</p>
</div>
<hr>
<p class="small">If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email — your password won't change until you click the link above and create a new one.</p>
<p class="small">If you're worried about your account security, <a href="{{supportUrl}}">contact support</a>.</p>
{{> footer}}
